<br>
What this guy is bringing to Fable was his methods of gradual visual change based on your style of play.  The changes in Black and White were so gradual, that 2/3 of the way through the game I was wondering when my temple was going to change.  I had to load a new game to realize that it had grown 10x as tall and grew spikes.  Not to mention the sky turning dark and cloudy.<br>
<br>
But that is what they say he is bringing in the Fable Trailer.  Start out with a base character, then everything you do affects the world:  how people react to you, and what you look like.  Choose magic and grow frail with arcane runes all over your skin, seeping magic.  Fight a lot and you get huge and muscular.  <br>
